## Description ##
Current v1.6.x branch contains some bugs in MKL-DNN Rnn operators that will cause gradients explosion in the Backward pass. https://github.com/apache/incubator-mxnet/pull/17183 has solved this problem. Besides, we also offered an enhancement for the Forward pass (https://github.com/apache/incubator-mxnet/pull/17075), which is prior to https://github.com/apache/incubator-mxnet/pull/17183. So we are expecting these two commits to be backported to v1.6.x branch.

@leezu @ptrendx @TaoLv Please take a review.
